<%- include('../partials/header') %>

<div class="auth-page">
  <div class="auth-card" style="max-width:480px;">
    <h2>Create Account</h2>
    <p class="auth-sub">Join Jikart</p>

    <form action="/auth/register" method="POST" id="registerForm">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Username</label>
        <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="Choose a username" required>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Email</label>
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email address" required>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Password</label>
        <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="At least 6 characters" required minlength="6">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Register as</label>
        <select name="role" onchange="toggleSellerNote(this)">
          <option value="buyer">Buyer (Student / Non-Student)</option>
          <option value="seller">Seller (Store Owner)</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div id="seller-note" class="info-box info-note" style="display:none; margin-bottom:16px;">
        <strong>Seller accounts require admin approval.</strong>
        After registering, an admin will review your account before you can log in and set up your store.
      </div>

      <!-- TERMS CHECKBOX -->
      <div class="form-group" style="margin-top:18px;">
        <label style="display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:10px; cursor:pointer; font-weight:400;">
          <input type="checkbox" id="agreeTerms" name="agree_terms" style="margin-top:3px; width:auto; flex-shrink:0;" required>
          <span style="font-size:0.88rem; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.5;">
            I have read and agree to the
            <a href="#" onclick="openTerms(); return false;" style="color:var(--primary); font-weight:600;">Terms & Policies</a>
            of Jikart.
          </span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-full" style="margin-top:8px;">Create Account</button>
    </form>

    <p class="auth-switch">Already have an account? <a href="/auth/login">Login here</a></p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TERMS MODAL -->
<div id="termsModal" class="modal hidden">
  <div class="modal-box" style="max-width:600px; text-align:left; max-height:85vh; overflow-y:auto;">
    <h3 style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; margin-bottom:4px;">Terms & Policies</h3>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted); font-size:0.82rem; margin-bottom:20px;">Jikart</p>

    <div class="terms-section">
      <h4>1. About the Platform</h4>
      <p>Jikart is a community-based online marketplace that connects student sellers, local sellers, and buyers within and around the campus community. All transactions are between individual users — Jikart provides the platform but is not directly involved in the buying and selling process.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="terms-section">
      <h4>2. Account Registration</h4>
      <p>You must provide accurate and truthful information when creating an account. Accounts found to have false or misleading information may be suspended or permanently removed.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Buyers</strong> must complete identity verification before placing any orders.</li>
        <li><strong>Sellers</strong> must wait for admin approval before accessing their store dashboard.</li>
        <li>You are responsible for keeping your password confidential.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="terms-section">
      <h4>3. Buyer Verification</h4>
      <p>All buyers are required to verify their identity before ordering. This helps protect sellers from fraudulent transactions and ensures a safe marketplace.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Students</strong> must submit a valid school ID photo, course, year level, and schedule.</li>
        <li><strong>Non-students</strong> must provide their occupation, workplace, and contact details.</li>
        <li>All buyers must provide a Facebook account link/name for dispute resolution purposes.</li>
        <li>Providing false verification information is grounds for immediate account suspension.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="terms-section">
      <h4>4. Ordering & Delivery</h4>
      <p>When placing an order, buyers must provide a valid delivery address within the campus or an agreed nearby location. Sellers have the right to confirm or reject any order.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Orders must be placed in good faith. Cancel only when absolutely necessary.</li>
        <li>Delivery time and date preferences may vary per seller and per order.</li>
        <li>Once an order is confirmed by the seller, the buyer is expected to be available to receive it.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="terms-section">
      <h4>5. Conduct & Fair Use</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Buy-tripping (placing orders with no intention to pay or receive) is strictly prohibited.</li>
        <li>Any form of harassment, fraud, or abuse towards sellers or other buyers will result in account suspension.</li>
        <li>Sellers must accurately describe their products and maintain enough stock.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="terms-section">
      <h4>6. Privacy</h4>
      <p>Your personal information (ID photo, contact number, Facebook account) is stored securely and is only accessible by platform admins for verification and dispute resolution purposes. It will never be shared with third parties.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="terms-section">
      <h4>7. Admin Authority</h4>
      <p>Admins reserve the right to approve, reject, suspend, or remove any account or listing that violates these terms or disrupts the community.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:24px; display:flex; gap:12px; justify-content:flex-end;">
      <button onclick="acceptTerms()" class="btn btn-primary">I Agree</button>
      <button onclick="closeTerms()" class="btn btn-cancel">Close</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
#termsModal {
  position: fixed !important;
  z-index: 9999 !important;
}

.terms-section {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.terms-section h4 {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: var(--secondary);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.terms-section p {
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.terms-section ul {
  padding-left: 18px;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.8;
}
</style>

<script>
function toggleSellerNote(sel) {
  document.getElementById('seller-note').style.display = sel.value === 'seller' ? 'block' : 'none';
}

function openTerms() {
  document.getElementById('termsModal').classList.remove('hidden');
}

function closeTerms() {
  document.getElementById('termsModal').classList.add('hidden');
}

function acceptTerms() {
  document.getElementById('agreeTerms').checked = true;
  closeTerms();
}

document.getElementById('termsModal').addEventListener('click', function(e) {
  if (e.target === this) closeTerms();
});
</script>

</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
